# Keep the build context small AND correct: excluding bin/obj is essential —
# otherwise the host's restored obj/ (project.assets.json) gets copied into the
# image and clobbers the in-container restore, causing "package not found" on
# publish --no-restore.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
.git/
.idea/
docs/
*.md
*.user
*.DotSettings.user
HomeDutiesAssistant/docker-compose.yml